flowchart TD
    A[Scaling Request] --> B{Horizontal or Vertical?}

    B -- Horizontal --> C[Add/remove TContainers]
    C --> D{Affects active refs/rounds?}
    D -- No --> E[Apply registry/topology update]
    D -- Yes --> F[Wait for safe point]

    B -- Vertical --> G[Prepare new uniform capacity profile]
    G --> H[Prepare new default empty container profile]
    H --> I[Invalidate old layout-bound refs]
    I --> J{All affected containers out of active rounds?}
    J -- No --> K[Wait for round completion]
    J -- Yes --> L[Claim profile-switch safe point]
    L --> M[Apply family-wide profile switch]
    M --> N[Moderator resets/reinitializes containers]
    N --> O[Emit scaling/profile reports]
